<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hearty" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hearty,</orth> 1) coming from the heart, sincere: <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.111" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. V, 111</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 5.4.74" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. V, 4, 74</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.2.99" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 2, 99</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 5.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas V, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.1.14" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B IV, 1, 14</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.3.82" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 3, 82</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 3.4.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. III, 4, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.6.228" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 6, 228</bibl>.<lb />2) kind-hearted, good-natured: <cit><quote>my h. friends, you take me in too dolorous a sense,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 4.2.38" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 2, 38</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>